1.name: Ore Refining
1.description: Ore Refining is used in many other recipes where refined metal is needed.  Metal Refining takes a single ore to complete the recipe.

8.name: Purified Water
8.description: Water once it has been purified can be drank.  Once the water is purified it can also be distilled to use in other recipes.

9.name: Distilled Water
9.description: Water once it has been distilled can be used as an agent in recipes.  It is also distilled to the state where it is not recommended to drink any more.

75.name: Engineer Species
75.description: Attempts to genetically engineer a species.

79.name: Motion Detection System
79.description: Motion Detection Systems can be used to create traps or alarms.

80.name: Metal Casing
80.description: Metal casing can be used to contain various cybernetic, explosive or electronic devices.

97.name: Pet Food
97.description: This would be a healthy meal for a pet.

198.name: Excess Fat Extraction
198.description: Removes the excess fat from the meat that is used in other recipes. It destroys the good part of the meat though so only use if you need the Fat.

199.name: Fruit Preperation
199.description: Extracts the fruit from the plant and prepares for it to be used/consumed.

203.name: Seed Extraction
203.description: Extracts the seeds from plants so they can be used.
